    • Method Detail

      • unordered

        DatabaseListableQueryBuilder unordered()
        If you haven't called orderBy(java.lang.String), the results of DatabaseListableQueryBuilder.list(java.sql.Connection, org.fluentjdbc.DatabaseResult.RowMapper<T>) will be unpredictable. Call unordered() if you are okay with this.

      • orderBy

        DatabaseListableQueryBuilder orderBy​(String orderByClause)
        Adds an order by clause to the query. Needed in order to list results in a predictable order.

        @Nonnull
<OBJECT> Optional<OBJECT> singleObject​(Connection connection,
                                       DatabaseResult.RowMapper<OBJECT> mapper)
